Section 1.1. .
Sale and Transfer of Shares
 
Subject to the terms and conditions of this Agreement, at the Closing, Go2Net shall sell, convey, assign, transfer and deliver to Purchaser, and Purchaser shall purchase from Go2Net, all the issued and outstanding Shares, free and clear of all Encumbrances, except for any Encumbrance arising under the Securities Act or any applicable state securities laws.
 
