Section 3.20. .
Tax Matters
 
(a) Each of the Company and the Company Subsidiary has timely filed (or there has been filed on its behalf) with appropriate taxing authorities all material Tax Returns required to be filed by it on or prior to the date hereof. All such Tax Returns were correct and complete in all material respects. All Taxes due and owing by the Company and the Company Subsidiary (whether or not shown on any Tax Return) have been paid. Neither the Company nor the Company Subsidiary currently is the beneficiary of any extension of time within which to file any Tax Return.
 
