requirement which would otherwise be applicable to any Transferred Employees and their eligible dependents on or after the Closing to the extent such Transferred Employee or eligible dependent had satisfied any similar limitation or requirement under an analogous Seller Plan prior to the Closing, and (iii) provide full credit under such plans for any deductibles, co-payments and out-of-pocket expenses incurred by Transferred Employees and their eligible dependents during the portion of the calendar year prior to such participation in which the Closing occurs
