(ii) Seller and its Subsidiaries shall not engage in any activity intended to discourage any Transferred Employee from accepting an offer of employment from Purchaser and/or its Designees and shall not offer employment with respect to any businesses of Seller or any
 
Subsidiary (other than the Business) after the date hereof and prior to the Closing Date; , , that Seller and its Subsidiaries shall be permitted to take any action they are legally required to take in order to comply with local labor and employment Laws;
