On May 11, 2010, InfoSpace, Inc. issued a press release announcing its entry into a new, specialty e-commerce channel and revising its second quarter 2010 guidance. A copy of the press release is attached hereto as Exhibits 99.1 and is incorporated herein by reference.
 
