InfoSpace will host a conference on January 9, 2012, at 5:30 a.m. Pacific time / 8:30 a.m. Eastern time to discuss the Merger. The live webcast and a copy of an investor presentation with additional information can be accessed in the Investor Relations section of the InfoSpace corporate website at http://www.infospaceinc.com. A copy of that investor presentation is attached hereto as Exhibit 99.2, and incorporated herein by reference.
 
