 with any such decision, act, consent or instruction. By way of amplification and not limitation, as Stockholder Representatives, the Stockholder Representatives shall be authorized and empowered, as agents of and on behalf of all stockholders and optionholders of the Company (only with respect to their interests as stockholders and optionholders) to give and receive notices and communications as provided herein, to object to any Acquiror Indemnification Claims, to agree to, negotiate, enter into
